snippet.title: VS. Zardy - New update. Bushwhack
snippet.description:
Wishlist Average4k (My new game) on steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1828580/Average4k/

Mod Link - https://gamebanana.com/mods/44366

After 5 months zardy finally gets a new update. Friday night funkin.

Though seriously, we're super proud of this and we hope you love it as much as we do :)

Zardy's new update is smth that took a bit to make.

but I cannot stress this enough, PLEASE play the original game https://store.steampowered.com/app/1484800/Zardys_Maze/
